        <h2>Dog Care Tips</h2>
        <p>Here are some essential tips for taking care of your dog:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Feeding: Offer a balanced diet specific to your dog's age, size, and health needs.</li>
            <li>Exercise: Ensure regular exercise to keep them fit and healthy.</li>
            <li>Regular Vet Visits: Keep up with vaccinations and check-ups.</li>
            <li>Grooming: Regular grooming keeps your dog clean and comfortable.</li>
            <li>Training: Basic obedience training is essential for a well-behaved pet.</li>
            <li>Socialization: Expose your dog to different people, animals, and environments.</li>
            <li>Love and Affection: Spend quality time with your pet for a happy and secure dog.</li>
        </ul>
